description: Case Logic is obsessed with organization! No matter who you are, what toys, tools or technology you have, where you are, or where you are going, Case Logic is your partner in managing the things that matter to you. We are the "stuff wranglers" that make life easier. With this focus in mind, Caselogic introduces the IPAD-101 Apple iPAD Sleeve. Compatible with Apple iPAD 9.7-Inch and tested to ensure perfect fit for your iPAD. Made with durable dobby nylon and 10mm foam to protect your iPAD from daily abuse. Ultra-suede grip facilitates easy removal from a backpack, bag or tote. Easy Access Zipper Closure and 25 Year Warranty!
title: Case Logic IPAD-101 Apple iPAD/iPAD2 Sleeve (Black)
